<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/boundary-commission-for-northern-ireland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Boundary Commission for Northern Ireland (BCNI) carries out boundary reviews of parliamentary constituencies in Northern Ireland, and submits its recommendations to the government. BCNI is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Northern Ireland Office ."@en .
